Almost a third of teachers have suffered online bullying at the hands of parents in the last year .
Families are using social media to post obscenities , threats , offensive photos , sexually explicit insults and teachers .
A study of 1,500 teachers found 30 per cent of teachers said they had been the subject of parents ' abusive internet posts .
The poll showed the proportion of teachers suffering abuse from parents and pupils has more than doubled over the past year .